\c 99
\s Jehovha mutsvene ngaarumbidzwe
\p
\v 99 Jehovha anobata ushe; vanhu ngavabvunde;
\s Iye agere pakati pamakerubhi; nyika ngaizununguswe.
\p
\v 2 Jehovha mukuru paZioni;
\s Ari kumusoro-soro kwavanhu vose.
\p
\v 3 Ngavarumbidze zita renyu guru rinotyisa;
\s Ndiye Mutsvene.
\p
\v 4 Simba ramambo rinodawo kururamisa;
\s Imi munosimbisa kururama, Munotonga muchiruramisa pakati paJakobho.
\p
\v 5 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, Munamate pachitsiko chetsoka dzake;
\s Ndiye Mutsvene.
\p
\v 6 Mosesi naAroni pakati pavapristi vake,
\s NaSamueri pakati pavanodana zita rake;
\s Vakadana kuna Jehovha, iye akavapindura.
\s Akataura navo ari mushongwe yegore;
\s Vakachengeta zvipupuriro zvake nomutemo waakavapa.
\p
\v 8 Makavapindura, Jehovha Mwari wedu;
\p Maiva Mwari aivakanganwira, Kunyange makatsiva zvavaiita.
\v 9 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, Namatai pagomo rake dzvene; Nokuti Jehovha Mwari wedu ndiye
\s Mutsvene.
